The paper focuses on the application of game theory in blockchain, which is a key aspect of the field of game theory (cs.GT). It also addresses security issues (cs.CR), mining management (cs.DC), economic and energy trading (cs.CY), and incentive mechanism design (cs.SI) in the context of blockchain. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
